  "prompt": "Did Luis von Ahn himself learn languages from Duolingo?",
  "response": "Luis von Ahn, the co-founder of Duolingo, mentioned in various interviews that while he has not extensively used Duolingo to learn a new language himself, he is proficient in several languages. Raised in Guatemala, he grew up speaking Spanish and learned English at a young age. His motivation for creating Duolingo was to make language education more accessible and effective for people worldwide. While he supports the mission and development of Duolingo, his personal language studies are not typically done through the app itself.",
